---
title: Ginger Beef Burger with Asian Slaw and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Inspired by a favourite Chinese Canadian dish hailing from Calgary, this burger is sure to please. Be careful if you've got your windows open while making these, you may just have your neighbours knocking, inquiring "what's for dinner?"
